705cd30f5ad0"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Izra\[CHacek]unajte vektorski produkt vektorjev (1, 2, 3) in (4, 5, 6) . \
Kolik\[SHacek]na je njegova dol\[ZHacek]ina? Nari\[SHacek]ite vse tri \
vektorje (ukaz ",
 StyleBox["Arrow",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 ") . "
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.984034327867035*^9, 
  3.984034344455868*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"085b2ce9-7dd7-45d1-bb36-\
a6e30ad99bc3"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Naloga 3", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.922962110423855*^9, 3.922962115556046*^9}, {
  3.983953614881898*^9, 3.9839536199810066`*^9}, {3.9840183495110197`*^9, 
  3.9840183549254527`*^9}, {3.9840342956605186`*^9, 
  3.9840343093890896`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"dee15b22-94f3-46fd-8d56-\
1b53410f332e"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Podan je sistem ena\[CHacek]b \n\t\[Beta] x + y - z = 1,\n\t2x + 5y = 9,\n\t\
y + z = -3.\nZapi\[SHacek]ite matriko sistema in se prepri\[CHacek]ajte, da \
je sistem re\[SHacek]ljiv za vsak \[Beta] razli\[CHacek]en od 4/5. Nato za \
\[Beta] = 1 re\[SHacek]ite sistem na dva na\[CHacek]ina: z ukazom ",
 StyleBox["LinearSolve",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " in ",
 StyleBox["Solve",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 ". "
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.984032623369055*^9, 3.9840326630329447`*^9}, {
  3.984032694031116*^9, 3.984032714394888*^9}, {3.984032748901335*^9, 
  3.9840328780770006`*^9}, {3.984034927036278*^9, 
  3.9840349391535873`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"bd1b9f72-fab3-47d8-a915-\
b10091683154"]
}, Open  ]]
}, Open  ]]
